--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5cdbdbb5164c5b1479a3eca103fc935d, type: 3}
  m_Name: 2_PremiersPas
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: 002
  lines:
  - speakerName: AXI
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 5978067422134562236, guid: 77184ec5a110d204882ecceb1e555656, type: 3}
    text: "Great, you know how to cast projectiles now!\r\nThe next step is to interact
      with this world. Walk up to the door and type \u201Cping view\u201D in your
      terminal."
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
  - speakerName: You
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 1751119502174200988, guid: 54ef6c48b4d05a3438e4973229e72209, type: 3}
    text: Okay, but before that, why are the leaves on the trees 0 and 1 ?
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
  - speakerName: AXI
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 5978067422134562236, guid: 77184ec5a110d204882ecceb1e555656, type: 3}
    text: Oh, that's not important, don't worry about it.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
  - speakerName: AXI
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 5978067422134562236, guid: 77184ec5a110d204882ecceb1e555656, type: 3}
    text: These are just system errors. Please continue.
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
  - speakerName: AXI
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 5978067422134562236, guid: 77184ec5a110d204882ecceb1e555656, type: 3}
    text: "Once you've typed the command \u201Cping view,\u201D you'll see the object's
      name, and then you can use \u201Ctoggle nearest\u201D"
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
  - speakerName: AXI
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 5978067422134562236, guid: 77184ec5a110d204882ecceb1e555656, type: 3}
    text: "I'll show you most of the commands, but if you want to learn more, try
      them out, type \u201Chelp\u201D."
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
